    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <strong>Q: What types of payment do you accept?</strong>
      <p>A: We currently accept <strong>cash, Zelle, Cash App, and Venmo</strong>. Credit/debit card payments will be available soon.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <strong>Q: Do you have a physical store?</strong>
      <p>A: No — Fix2Go is a fully <strong>mobile repair service</strong>. We come to your location, whether it’s your home, office, or a public place.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <strong>Q: What areas do you serve?</strong>
      <p>A: We currently serve <strong>Tampa, Brandon, Riverview, Wesley Chapel, St. Pete, and nearby neighborhoods</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <strong>Q: What devices do you repair?</strong>
      <p>A: We repair <strong>iPhones, Android phones, tablets, laptops, and game consoles</strong>. We specialize in screen repairs, battery replacements, and more.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <strong>Q: How do I book an appointment?</strong>
      <p>A: Visit our <a href="/book-appointment">Book Appointment</a> page to schedule a repair. We’ll confirm with you via email or text.</p>
